{"tid":1531351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online功略 「長期置頂」","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:23:53.000Z","uid":173612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5874a8e9f20c85e723e233dd3949c5ef6d0a637e","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"活動去到呢一刻 無可否認我哋 <span style=\"color: red;\">和理非 勇武 文宣</span>都遇到唔少問題<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非遇到嘅問題</span><br />\n<br />\n首先和理非面對住濃厚嘅白色恐怖 返工嘅驚比人炒（好似國泰） 遊行嘅驚比人拉 所以會令到唔少人自我審查 唔出嚟 唔出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議</span><br />\n<br />\n首先唔好分化佢哋 好似國泰 黨鐵咁 大家唔好只話佢做咩唔罷工 唔反抗 講就容易 你養佢哋？ 一間大公司你要拎佢跪低要用好長時間 呢段時間係唔係你support佢哋? 所以你屌9佢哋都無意思 咁樣只係令到我哋嘅同路人越來越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我建議成立一個基金 眾所周知香港人嘅眾籌能力相當之高 呢個基金專門去幫助一啲受到白色恐怖打壓嘅人 佢哋可以喺基金裏面攞一啲生活費解決燃眉之急 等到佢哋唔會覺得自己係condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者我鼓勵唔少中少企老闆或有能力決定請人嘅人幫幫手 向受到白色恐怖嘅打壓者伸出援手 當呢啲人受到打壓 解雇嘅時候 你幫佢一把 長遠而言可以鞏固到同路人之間嘅聯繫同團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 我仍然覺得和理非要揸緊機場春袋 始終機場對香港影響實在太大 所以我希望大家唔好放棄呢一個咁重要嘅春袋 係機場我覺得唔好整RB 唔好帶gear 唔好比位狗入 我哋就話佢知 我哋真係嚟坐巴士 機鐵 揸車我係鐘意唔行自動交錢 你吹啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錯雖然咁樣仍然係有機會俾人拉（你知依家啲狗幾on9) 但又點 你無做犯法野驚乜 最多咪48個鐘 當然你話可能係48個鐘入邊俾人打 你淆淆豬 咁就要睇你唔願意為香港 為自己 為下一代踏出呢一步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就你真係過唔到自己心理過關 你都可以做文宣嘢為香港出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">勇武遇到嘅問題</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然我認為勇武未必會上連登睇... 但都講吓啦 我認為而家勇武代價太高 我唔係話叫散水或者係退場呢啲on9嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但各位勇武 你哋要諗下你哋少一個就真係少一個 再加上UC9 武力差距咁大 你哋真係要萬分小心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都知勇武係乜撚都唔驚 所以唔好講咩叫佢唔好出嚟呢啲on9嘢 我哋只要課金比佢哋就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論係星火 612基金 買裝 人哋出血 我哋出錢 抵！<br />\n<br />\n另外勇武亦都要諗下再係咁怒火街頭係唔係唯一方法呢？如果區區組成民間保護隊 有老黑出現就打柒佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />市民一方會唔會就更加支持你地呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋得閒又可以接下放學 麻包袋嗰啲就唔好亂搞到啲狗官同狗啦 好暴力架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（但核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n仲有啊如果勇武訓唔著又點好啊精力得唔到發洩 咁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪去叫下狗起身屙下夜尿 起身屌閪lo 友善提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正<br />\n<br />\n所以勇武要諗下係唔係次次都仲要怒火街頭 你要發洩精力仲有好多嘢玩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣方面</span><br />\n<br />\n呢方面我就真係唔熟 唔識點吸引人哋 但係呢我發現到連儂牆有啲資料實在太舊 我覺得可重建一下 換返啲新嘅 唔好呢個時候仲只係見到香蕉糖 應該仲有好多新人值得表揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但注意夜晚好多痴線佬 各位連儂牆手足應該搵埋勇武BB一齊 話唔埋結良緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋好多香港市民唔明白攬炒嘅原因 攬炒嘅背後意思 同埋攬炒點樣會成功達致光復香港 我相信要好好向市民解釋我哋攬炒並唔係破壞香港 係建設重建香港 先安內後<br />\n攘外 我哋需要喺香港要有股攬炒風氣有共識 先可以團結向外國宣稱香港已經準備好 if we burn , you burn with us. <br />\n<br />\n另外我要大讚民間記者會 越做越好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋需要你哋幫我地拆穿政府嘅謊言 唔好比政府一言堂繼續向市民洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續加油<br />\n<br />\n最後外國戰線 我相信攬炒巴等團隊比我更為熟悉所以唔多講 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位睇到嚟呢到 歡迎各位討論 要屌麻煩屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1304eb0bca6c431351c83ee314bc58c8b7ece3f","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"十連開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dec65867ce5e689c5ebc5ee7ac557591ccedf2d","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22bb10e00d7d5df218edfdd5ab24dcae12cecab","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:49:59.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59402af936f8f5b3bdc587aa721441ef73af7860","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da2613e52363f74ad6aa6a4a3c2e70dba302a10","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3548d58700cdfc8ca60109e5148ebc7922e320","tid":1531351,"uid":76538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:50:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">阻一阻你, 幫手入去睇下, 救下學生</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n［學校戰線］打壓學生中學名單！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1531335/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1531335/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2f982c7d0a34b7efc856478f58295e9f43fc3876","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b394f41a0076b7a879b86ebbb8bc8dfd955936","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b7c5960bbccadfc0d31347eb0ebe18c22547c1","tid":1531351,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵者，詭道也。故能而示之不能，用而示之不用，近而示之遠，遠而示之近。利而誘之，亂而取之，實而備之，強而避之，怒而撓之，卑而驕之，佚而勞之，親而離之，攻其不備，出其不意。此兵家之勝，不可先傳也。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>兵者詭道也</strong><br />\n用兵之道在於千變萬化<br />\n<strong>能而示之不能，用而示之不用</strong><br />\n隱藏真正的實力或者是讓不欲人知的訊息隱藏不露<br />\n<strong>近而示之遠，遠而示之近</strong><br />\n將主力或即將要發動的攻勢，佯裝到錯誤的距離及位置，令敵人評估失準<br />\n<strong>利而誘之</strong><br />\n用利益引誘貪利之人<br />\n<strong>亂而取之</strong><br />\n製造混亂，然後再乘虛而入<br />\n<strong>實而備之</strong><br />\n以充足的準備，去面對軍隊整齊有實力的對手<br />\n<strong>強而避之</strong><br />\n對強大士氣旺盛的敵人，先避其鋒，待其疲憊，再尋求反擊的機會<br />\n<strong>怒而撓之</strong><br />\n不斷騷擾敵人，令其破綻百出<br />\n<strong>卑而驕之</strong><br />\n以卑微的態度，令自大的對手失去危機感<br />\n<strong>佚而勞之</strong><br />\n以逸待勞，以最佳狀態迎接奔波疲勞的敵人<br />\n<strong>親而離之</strong><br />\n接近敵人的親信，然後進行離間行為，令其內外孤立<br />\n<strong>攻其不備</strong><br />\n攻擊對手無防備，或較薄弱的地方<br />\n<strong>出其不意</strong><br />\n在對手意想不到的地方及情勢下發動攻擊<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"d4571b703955b1a34ea99c474a1d48b22e94b619","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"再十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3f63fd1adb7e248d32a4631a8a97f05ca5eb00","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156da251f3471121c994be07627daabccff8be27","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07863cecbbd7f6d09f7fe571e5ee3f3316301348","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191ae6b18a166c5af7de5b8961e9a6531ac22b85","tid":1531351,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/